    <author initials="M." surname="Sethi" fullname="Mohit Sethi">
      <organization>Ericsson</organization>
    </author>
    <date day="05" month="March" year="2018"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies the use of EAP-TLS with TLS 1.3 while
   remaining backwards compatible with existing implementations of EAP-
   TLS.  TLS 1.3 provides significantly improved security, privacy, and
   reduced latency when compared to earlier versions of TLS.</t>
